sentences.english: Every family will pack the silkworm eggs in paper, and start to hatch them.
sentences.chinese: 家家戶戶將蠶種紙包好，開始孵蠶卵。

sentences.english: At present, pebrine influence seriously on the egg-production of silkworm.
sentences.chinese: 目前家蠶微粒子病對蠶種生產造成很大影響。

sentences.english: Note :Sources is from Guangdong Province silkworm eggs inspection station.
sentences.chinese: 資料來源爲廣東省蠶種質檢站。
